code: function GetNationalId(nationalId,length){if(nationalId==null)return null;if(typeof nationalId!="string"||nationalId.length!=length)return null;var digits=[];for(var index=0;index<nationalId.length;index++){var digit=nationalId[index];if(isNaN(digit))return null;var digitSet=new Set(nationalId);if(digitSet.size===1)return null;else digits.push(parseInt(digit));}return digits;}export function IsLegalPersonNationalIdValid(nationalId){var digits=GetNationalId(nationalId,11);if(digits==null)return false;var ratio1=digits[9]+2;var ratioes=[29,27,23,19,17];var sum=0;for(var index=0;index<digits.length-1;index++){sum+=(ratio1+digits[index])*ratioes[index%5];}sum%=digits.length;if(sum==10)sum=0;return sum==digits[digits.length-1];}export function IsRealPersonNationalIdValid(nationalId){var digits=GetNationalId(nationalId,10);if(digits==null)return false;var sum=0;for(var index=0;index<digits.length-1;index++){sum+=digits[index]*(10-index);}sum%=11;if(sum>=2)sum=11-sum;return sum==digits[digits.length-1];}
